column2: SELECT          n.distance,pz.*,o.gain_u,o.gain_g,o.gain_r,o.gain_i,o.gain_z,o.saturationLevel_u,o.saturationLevel_g         ,o.saturationLevel_r,o.saturationLevel_i,o.saturationLevel_z         FROM PhotoObjAll  as pz         JOIN dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( #,#,         #)          AS n ON pz.objid = n.objid              JOIN Field AS o ON pz.FieldID=o.FieldID         ORDER by n.distance
